To update fragment in ViewPager, we should call PagerAdapter.notifyDataSetChanged() when data changed. we should also override FragmentPagerAdapter.getItemPosition(), and implement a public method for updating fragment.   Refer to [Update Fragment from ViewPager](http://stackoverflow.com/a/18088509/2722270)
